  "markdown_content": "\n## Executive Summary\n\nUser requested testing and demonstration of the Wix connector capabilities. Manus successfully tested the connector, identified 13 available tools across site management, e-commerce, and documentation categories. Demonstrated practical functionality by listing 13 Wix sites, retrieving site properties from 'wcw-test' site (CHF currency, Europe/Zurich timezone), and accessing documentation search capabilities.\n\n\n## Context & Intent\n\nUser wanted to understand and test the Wix connector functionality, requesting practical examples and feature overview\n\n\n## What Was Done\n\nComprehensive testing of Wix MCP connector including tool enumeration, site listing, API calls to retrieve site properties, and documentation search demonstrations\n\n\n## Outputs Produced\n\n- [report] Wix Connector Capabilities Report — Comprehensive overview of 13 Wix tools categorized by function\n- [demonstration] Live API Testing Results — Real data retrieval from wcw-test site showing configuration details\n- [documentation] Best Practices Guide — Workflow recommendations for using Wix connector effectively\n\n## Key Decisions & Validations\n\n- Demonstrated live API calls rather than just listing capabilities\n- Structured response by tool categories for clarity\n- Included practical examples with real site data\n\n## Lessons Learned\n\nWorked well:\n\n- Connector responded successfully to all test operations\n- Documentation search functionality works as expected\n- Site management tools provide comprehensive site access\nDiscoveries:\n\n- Connector provides 13 specialized tools across multiple Wix domains\n- Real site data shows CHF currency and Swiss timezone configuration\n- Documentation tools cover REST API, SDK, and design system components\n\n## Open Questions\n\n- What specific Wix operations does the user want to automate?\n- Are there particular e-commerce or booking features to explore further?\n\n## Next Steps\n\n- Await user feedback on specific Wix operations of interest\n- Explore e-commerce or booking functionality if relevant to user needs\n- Consider integration with other tools based on user requirements\n---\nUID: BLNnVBGbhjx7CjjgBfCtAX | Model: claude-sonnet-4-20250514 | Cost: $0.0135\n"
